OL,3,CDouble jeopardy killer Billy Dunlop to
OL,4,Chave public parole hearing
OL,6,FThe next parole hearing for double
OL,7,Fjeopardy killer Billy Dunlop is to be
OL,8,Fpublic the Parole Board have confirmed.
OL,10,FWilliam Dunlop, 63, who is known as
OL,11,FBilly, strangled Julie Hogg in
OL,12,FBillingham, County Durham, in 1989 and
OL,13,Fhid her mutilated body behind a bath
OL,14,Fpanel in her own home, where it lay
OL,15,Fundiscovered for more than two months.
OL,17,FDunlop subjected the 22-year-old, who
OL,18,Fhad a three-year-old son, to what
OL,19,Fprosecutors described as a
OL,20,F"premeditated and truly horrendous"
OL,21,Fattack after she rejected him.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@cO]
