OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1780938366
OL,3,CDouble jeopardy killer Billy Dunlop to
OL,4,Chave public parole hearing
OL,6,FThe murderer had boasted there was
OL,7,Fnothing anyone could do to bring him
OL,8,Fto justice because the law at the time
OL,9,Fprevented him being tried more than
OL,10,Fonce for the same crime.
OL,12,FIn statement today (4 June) a
OL,13,Fspokesperson for the Parole Board told
OL,14,FITV Tyne Tees: "A judicial Parole
OL,15,FBoard member, on behalf of the Chair
OL,16,Fof the Parole Board, has granted the
OL,17,Fapplication for William Dunlop's
OL,18,Fparole hearing to be made public.
OL,26,@vD@POU
