PN,42704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1780938366
OL,3,CDouble jeopardy killer Billy Dunlop to
OL,4,Chave public parole hearing
OL,6,F"Parole Board decisions are solely
OL,7,Ffocused on what risk a prisoner could
OL,8,Frepresent to the public if released
OL,9,Fand whether that risk is manageable in
OL,10,Fthe community. "
OL,12,FThe hearing itself will take place
OL,13,Fwith the parties, the Panel and
OL,14,Fwitnesses at a secure location, with
OL,15,Farrangement made for members of the
OL,16,Fpublic to view the hearing remotely at
OL,17,Fa place where they will be able to
OL,18,Fmore easily attend.
OL,20,FThe hearing is to take place in
OL,21,FOctober 2026.
